{
  "stem": "27031.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But as it worked out, that's the only people that were lucky.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They survived by sending them to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But at that time, we were not too comfortable with the Soviets, neither.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father tried to run away when the Germans were coming closer to our village, but it was too late.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Soviets informed us that they were taking the Germans, they're winning the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't tell us that the Germans are next door already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the propaganda was that they're winning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we didn't-- the Germans came in so quickly, we didn't have a chance to-- to run away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's when hell started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I would-- should we start from the beginning?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That will take me two hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When the Germans came in, the first thing that I can remember-- I was 11 years old, approximately-- and the first hardship they did is every Jew had to wear a yellow badge on the front, and one in the back.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They shamed us in front of the Gentile people walking the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were recognized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And secondly, they took us out of school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A Jew couldn't go to public school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Couldn't go to any school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We went-- under hiding, we went to the Hebrew school, which it was in no longer in a synagogue, but was in a private house of the-- of the teacher.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] The Germans was in from '41.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The war started in '41, in about June.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were there until March '44.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, uh-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] There was lots of different things that went through, like our parents told us that there's going to be hardships.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
